(77275, 1892, 6411, 17, 'From Border to Border 1949 邊界到邊界 1949', '曲：鍾玉鳳\nWritten by Chung Yufeng\n演奏：Wolfgang Obrecht\nPerformed by Wolfgang Obrecht\n紀錄片主要的歷史口述者鍾河芳說：「回不去了，印度就變成我們的母國。」\nAs one of the main interviewees in the film, Paul Chung, says, "We cannot go back. India has become our mother country."\n', '2014-07-23 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 7, '', '', 33, '', '', '', '鍾適芳', '大大樹音樂圖像', '', 1, 1, 0, '2014-07-07 14:59:30', '2015-03-12 14:07:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77276, 1892, 6411, 19, 'Last Stop 終站', '「這一天，我們在加爾各答」電影音樂現場錄音\n影音素材：「邊界移動兩百年」\n即興：Wolfgang Obrecht、鍾玉鳳、大竹研\n曲：姚敏 （天上人間）\nLive Recording\nMelody is an excerpt from "Paradise and Earth” by Yao Min\nImprovised performance by Wolfgang Obrecht (Accordion), Chung Yufeng (Pipa) and Ken Ohtake (Electric Guitar) \n\n\n對於多數的印度華人來說，生命是沒有終站的旅行，他們不斷起錨航向另一個未知，尋找最後一個碼頭。\nThere is no final destination for many of the Indian Chinese. One could say that their journey is a series of unknown destinations.\n', '2014-07-23 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 7, '', '', 610, '', '姚敏', '', '鍾適芳', '大大樹音樂圖像', '', 1, 1, 0, '2014-07-07 14:59:53', '2015-03-12 14:07:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77277, 1892, 6411, 14, 'Parade 遊行', '音景：2013 Ballygunge社區、2012-2013 塔壩\nSoundscape: Recorded in the Ballygunge District (2013) and Tangra (2012 and 2013)\n\n\n城南的公寓，擴音器測試擾亂了清晨，電流的噪音斷斷續續，接著揚起 Lata Mangeshkar演唱的愛國歌曲Ae Mere Watan Ke Logon（祖國的人民）。鼓樂隊在公寓前的窄巷行進，這一天是印度獨立紀念日，全邦沸騰著旗幟與口號。華人沈默，專注迎接中國新年，排練世代傳乘的獅鼓。獅的舞蹈從沒有那麼貼近並真實，加爾各答塔壩年夜的拍攝，一夜一天沒有停機。兒時讀物中的傳統年夜，家家戶戶守歲，舞獅到天光，原來還在這裡，離家很遠的印度。\n\n\nAt the Ballygunge apartments, a loudspeaker awakens the neighborhood. A noisy, crackling speaker blasts Lata Mangeshkar''s patriotic song "Ae Mere Watan Ke Longon" ("O! The People of My Country"). A drumming troupe gathers in a narrow alley: It''s Independence Day in India, flags are flying and slogans are being chanted. Meanwhile, a group of Chinese in another neighborhood are preoccupied with the upcoming Lunar New Year celebrations. They have a drum corp of their own, a Lion Dance troupe, who have been practicing around the clock for their upcoming performance. \n', '2014-07-23 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 7, '', '', 98, '', '', '', '鍾適芳', '大大樹音樂圖像', '', 1, 1, 0, '2014-07-07 15:09:43', '2015-03-12 14:07:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
